author: Top Gear
description:
One minute, fourteen seconds, point eight. Or 1:14.8. Either way, that’s the top-20 lap time set in 2024 by The Stig in the Porsche 992 GT3 RS. But now, having been recently bested at the Top Gear Test Track by the Ford Mustang GTD, it’s back, and sporting the Manthey performance kit upgrade. It’s a £100,000 extra, but can all those wings, wheel covers and trick suspension make it faster than before, and faster than the Mustang GTD?

🚗 Porsche 911 (992.1) GT3 RS Manthey
